content.description: Great sit start with a low undercling for your left hand and high crimp for you right. The crux is getting into position to get the heel hook to finalize the send. Great location, being in the shade for most of the day and the sound of the creek below. good piggy back trip off of Dam Straight area. Worth the extra 2 min hike.
content.location: Continue on the main trail on the dam heading south, and then look for a trial on your right (west) that heads off past the red posts. After the branch off of the main trail, continue going west for about 25 yards till you get to the last prominent rock formation. right on the other side of that is Dead Reckoning.
